import './Roadmap.css'; import React from 'react'; export const Roadmap = () => { return (
THE GAME PLAN
Building an inter-connected community is our number one priority. We strive for greatness and embrace risk-taking, hustling and seizing every moment.
PRE-MINT PHASE
Our goal pre-mint is to create and foster a community that encourages our members to win and thrive. We see ourselves as the pioneers of the Web3 space, the Ballers of the digital world. Once our team of Ballers is formed we’ll move forward as a united front to show rest of the world what we can do.
PHASE ONE
Baller Games
To grow closer as a community and reward our holders, we’ll host fun, interactive games and giveaways. Ballers will compete in weekly tournaments for NFTs, ETH Prizes and whitelist opportunities.
Ballers-Only Event (+2 guest)
The in-person Ballers-Only Event will be filled with giveaways and other Baller fun. This will be an opportunity to connect on a deeper level as a community and encourage greater connectivity among Ballers.
PHASE TWO
The Baller Bank
5% of our primary mint will be allocated to community funds and put in the Baller Bank. The Baller Society holders will have the influence to decide what to do with these funds.
PHASE THREE
The Baller Society Brand
To a baller, fashion is about more than simply covering up. Clothes are an extension of personality, emotion and self. The ballers use fashion to exert their confidence and trademark their look. To encourage the passion of self-expression in our holders, we plan to create the most exclusive and stylish look, sure to bring out the Baller in all of us.
PHASE FOUR
The Baller-Gauntlet Airdrop
Every holder will have the chance to obtain the baller-gauntlet as a reward for maintaining your Baller NFT. The all powerful Gauntlet, made out of the same meteor that brought the ballers to life, can be used to ameliorate/transform your Baller and can also be used to redeem gifts from future partnerships.
PHASE FIVE
); };
